cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DC 

The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques to identify artefacts in polarimetric images. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for classification makes it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of transfer learning, which is a popular technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
